{
  "stem": "1938.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my, my parents went to the sister what she lives with, and, and they give her gold and whatever that she is good to me, that she gives me something, but it never, it never, it never worked.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Never worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was very, very depressed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So one time, an SS man from our camp came out and having-- to have fun.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What he did, he, he told us, who has complaints to come out and say.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was very naive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES] And I came, I came into concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If we have complaints.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just for fun.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said, just for the sake that I am one child to my parents, suffered so much-- I, I was too naive-- I would like to, to get out.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was beaten up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was two weeks laying almost dead from-- swollen and black and blue.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the fun of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were laughing and making fun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was a-- Yeah?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1,000.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--a lot of people in the camp, 1,000 women.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1,000.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just women.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the last years came in few men--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to another--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in the beginning, it was just-- and when they beat you up, it was just women.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just women.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, we have one room, big, big, and we have three bed, one on the other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were working a night shift or day shift.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were making material for blankets for the Wehrmacht, for the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We learned this profession in six weeks, which other German women, it took two or three years.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he was very upset about it, this SS man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, [NON-ENGLISH] how come the Jewish are so-- can, can--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--learn so fast?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was outrageous mad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for this reason, he came every Sunday.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
